@prefix prov: <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#> .
@prefix time: <http://www.w3.org/2006/time#> .
@prefix gn: <https://www.geonames.org/ontology#> .
@prefix BBO: <https://www.irit.fr/recherches/MELODI/ontologies/BBO#> .

# Base URI for instances
@base <https://w3id.org/noria/instances/> .

# =============================================================================
# KOS Concepts (Knowledge Organization System)
# These are not part of the NORIA ontology itself but are used as ranges for properties.
# =============================================================================

# Application Types
<https://w3id.org/noria/kos/application/type/infrastructure> a skos:Concept ; rdfs:label "Infrastructure Application"@en .
<https://w3id.org/noria/kos/application/type/business> a skos:Concept ; rdfs:label "Business Application"@en .
<https://w3id.org/noria/kos/application/type/monitoring> a skos:Concept ; rdfs:label "Monitoring Application"@en .
<https://w3id.org/noria/kos/application/type/database> a skos:Concept ; rdfs:label "Database Application"@en .
<https://w3id.org/noria/kos/application/type/security> a skos:Concept ; rdfs:label "Security Application"@en .

# Application Business Importance
<https://w3id.org/noria/kos/application/business-importance/critical> a skos:Concept ; rdfs:label "Critical Business Importance"@en .
<https://w3id.org/noria/kos/application/business-importance/high> a skos:Concept ; rdfs:label "High Business Importance"@en .
<https://w3id.org/noria/kos/application/business-importance/medium> a skos:Concept ; rdfs:label "Medium Business Importance"@en .
<https://w3id.org/noria/kos/application/business-importance/low> a skos:Concept ; rdfs:label "Low Business Importance"@en .

# Application Module Status
<https://w3id.org/noria/kos/application/status/InProduction> a skos:Concept ; rdfs:label "In Production"@en .
<https://w3id.org/noria/kos/application/status/Development> a skos:Concept ; rdfs:label "In Development"@en .
<https://w3id.org/noria/kos/application/status/Maintenance> a skos:Concept ; rdfs:label "In Maintenance"@en .
<https://w3id.org/noria/kos/application/status/Decommissioned> a skos:Concept ; rdfs:label "Decommissioned"@en .

# Service Types
<https://w3id.org/noria/kos/service/type/CustomerFacingService> a skos:Concept ; rdfs:label "Customer Facing Service"@en .
<https://w3id.org/noria/kos/service/type/ResourceFacingService> a skos:Concept ; rdfs:label "Resource Facing Service"@en .
<https://w3id.org/noria/kos/service/type/InternalService> a skos:Concept ; rdfs:label "Internal Service"@en .

