<https://w3id.org/noria/kos/TroubleTicket/severity/Warning> a skos:Concept ; rdfs:label "Warning Severity"@en .

# Trouble Ticket Type
<https://w3id.org/noria/kos/TroubleTicket/type/Failure> a skos:Concept ; rdfs:label "Failure Ticket"@en .
